text: Diep.io is a multiplayer browser game created by Matheus Valadares in 2016. In this simple browser game, cells try to eat agar and other cells to grow bigger. The game became popular on the internet, especially on YouTube, and attracted millions of players every day. It became the most played video game of 2015. A company from Switzerland called Miniclip made a mobile version of the game. Category:.io video games
title: Diep.io
